summary:
just a little reminder to those who think that live action Mewtwo looks weird. 
Mewtwo is, as far as we can tell, based off of a...
body:
just a little reminder to those who think that live action Mewtwo looks weird.

Mewtwo is, as far as we can tell, based off of a sphynx cat. one of these little guys.

as hairless cats, they are already kinda weird looking.

(tho I think theyre cute)

regardless it isn’t too big a stretch to turn that into this

Mewtwo just has more exaggeratedly human features as a product of science. mainly in his chest and fingers.

but the rest? definitely a hairless cat.
